The Glenn Beck Radio Show OCT-14-2013 MON




The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET   

      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 10/14/13


Monday, October 14, 2013 11:25 AM



Glenn feels we are on the verge of economic collapse 
 and just like in the 19th century the Republican party was born from the ashes of the Whigs,
 it is now time for a new party to rise from the ashes of the Republican party.

  Also, Bob Costas goes on a politically correct rant about the name and moniker
  of the Washington Redskins, and Glenn shares his feelings about that.

  Plus, the reason behind the disruption of the EBT system over the weekend,
      and as always it's time to #DefundtheGOP.
